Delivering the premium value in coal
We are WESTMORELAND COAL COMPANY.  We offer state-of-the-art mining techniques and uncompromised safety to our employees.  We are award-winning environmental stewards of the land we mine.  Westmoreland Coal is diversified, ethical and committed to our employees, customers, shareholders, and partners.
